        <div class="text bio">
          <p>We don't have a bio. If we did, it would touch on the fact that we're two animals and a nerd. It would also somehow incorporate this conversation overheard between mother and child right before Ereptile Destruction played Rippers on Rockaway Beach:</p>

          <p><strong>Junior:</strong> Mama, what’s an Ereptile?</p>
          <p><strong>Mother:</strong> Well son, that’s a little hard to explain.</p>
          <p><strong>Junior:</strong> Whats a Destruction?</p>
          <p><strong>Mother:</strong> That’s when something blows up and and chunks of shit go flying everywhere.</p>
          <p><strong>Junior:</strong> Mama, what’s Ereptile Destruction?</p>
          <p><strong>Mother:</strong> Well son, that's a garage metal trio from Brooklyn, NY.</p>
          <p><strong>Junior:</strong> Are they any good?</p>
          <p><strong>Mother:</strong> What if the sun emitted sound instead of light?</p>
          <p><strong>Junior:</strong> Your ears would go blind?</p>
          <p><strong>Mother:</strong> Yes, son.</p>
          <p><strong>Junior:</strong> Wow they are good.</p>
          <p><strong>Mother:</strong> Yes, son.</p>
        </div>
